      "writtenOn": "2019-03-12T16:51:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think it just means creating a repo like the GitBuilder example repo with more commits on each branch. E.g.\n\n0 - 1 - 2 - 4 - 5 ---- 7 - 8\n      \\-- 3 ----- 6 -/\n\nThen verify that:\n - The result is topo. sorted\n - 0 and 1 are adjacent\n - 2, 4, and 5 are adjacent\n - 3 and 6 are adjacent\n - 7 and 8 are adjacent\n\nI think that\u0027s all that is implied by \"avoid showing commits on multiple lines of history intermixed.\"",
