      "writtenOn": "2019-03-11T20:13:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "That\u0027s true, but mostly I was just worried about weird edge cases and test coverage. I can understand \"from-to\" much better (or at least I think I do...).",
      "parentUuid": "fbcf56ee_c7dbc286",
      "range": {
